n)." ALK Laboratories Inc, Wallingford, CT.', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Trastuzumab emtansine, Panitumumab, Ipilimumab, Necitumumab, Bevacizumab, Dostarlimab, Amivantamab, Ramucirumab, More', NULL, 1767369485);
