ug-drug interactions for use in electronic health records." J Am Med Inform Assoc 19 (2012): 735-43[7] "Product Information. Camptosar (irinotecan)." Pharmacia and Upjohn, Kalamazoo, MI.[8] "Product Information. Juxtapid (lomitapide)." Aegerion Pharmaceuticals Inc, Cambridge, MA.', 'Acalabrutinib, Dacomitinib, Tepotinib, Avapritinib, Bosutinib, Selumetinib, Vandetanib, Cobimetinib, Ibrutinib, Afatinib, Tivozanib, More', NULL, 1767369485);
