 formularies (vidal, british national formulary)." Drug Saf 30 (2007): 1063-71[5] "Product Information. Exelon (rivastigmine)" Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[6] "Product Information. Aricept (donepezil)." Pfizer US Pharmaceuticals, New York, NY.', 'Celecoxib', 'Memantine, Ginkgo biloba, Aducanumab', 1767369485);
